@(130-135=c1815.130) (@wPN{Ḫuwawa} addressed @wRN{Gilgameš}:) @q[Huwawa,Gilgamec]{“So come on now, you heroic bearer of a sceptre of wide-ranging power! Noble glory of the gods, angry bull standing ready for a fight! Your mother knew well how to bear sons, and your nurse knew well how to nourish children on the breast! Don't be afraid, rest your hand on the ground!”}

@(136-139=c1815.136) @wRN{Gilgameš} rested his hand on the ground, and addressed @wPN{Ḫuwawa}: @q[Gilgamec,Huwawa]{“By the life of my own mother @wDN{Ninsumun} and of my father, holy @wDN{Lugalbanda}! No one really knows where in the mountains you live; they would like to know where in the mountains you live. Here, I have brought you @wPN{En-me-barage-si}, my big sister, to be your wife in the mountains.”}

@(140-144=c1815.140) And again he addressed him: @q[Gilgamec,Huwawa]{“By the life of my mother @wDN{Ninsumun} and of my father, holy @wDN{Lugalbanda}! No one really knows where in the mountains you live; they would like to know where in the mountains you live. Here, I have brought you @wPN{Ma-tur}, my little sister, to be your concubine in the mountains. Just hand over your terrors to me! I want to become your kinsman!”}

